    "The second largest eigenvalue ofA α, λ 2 (A α)In addition to analyzing the α-index of the k-path graphs with k = 2, 3, 4 and bounded order, it was considered to evaluate λ 2 (A α), the second largest eigenvalue of A α (G), for α ∈ {0.1,..., 0.9}.",
    "Tables 9 and 10 present the graphs, in g6 format and their respective color sequences, that have the maximum λ 2 (A α) (for α ∈ {0.1,..., 0.9}) among the 2-path graphs of fixed order n. Each row in the tables represents the order of the graph.",
